  "title": "Greenhouse - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "The Greenhouse is a building present on the farm from the start. It is initially in a state of disrepair, making it unusable. It can be repaired by completing the Pantry Bundles for the Community Center or by purchasing \"Greenhouse\" from the Joja Community Development Form for data-sort-value=\"35000\">35,000g. Once repaired, it can be moved by talking to Robin at the Carpenter's Shop.",
